title: James House - Home Part 1 [2009]
description: James House is a songwriter who has the gift of telling a story, in such a descriptive way, that makes you feel like the song was written for your feelings. Still in the game- Should be the the theme song for a Nike commerical. Tiger Woods- with a nike (Just do it) logo as the song ends. That song can portray anybodys life. If I had my way, Hard times for a honest man, all great songs. Roy Orbison, Hank Williams, wrote these kind of songs and James has this kind of talen
